title: Jimbo Presents: It's My Special Show!
overview: Join RuPaul's Drag Race All Stars 8 Winner Jimbo as she clowns around in her own special studio - interviewing esteemed guests, playing out-of-this-world games, and taking it to the streets of Hollywood. Grab a front row seat into the mind of the world's first self-proclaimed Drag Clown. It's My Special Show!
